  "description": "The first film in the six-part <i>Girls und Panzer: Saishuushou</i> film series.<br>\n<br>\nToo much tankery and not enough studying for her entrance exams has landed Momo in the hot seat! Luckily her friends won’t let her flunk out without a fight, and they’ve hatched a foxy plan to put her back on top. Miho’s stepping down to let Momo take up the mantle of commander, because if she can lead the team to victory in the Continuous Cup, Momo can retake her exams. The stakes have never been higher for the team as they fight for tank supremacy both on and off the combat field!<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Sentai Filmworks)",
